title: I'm in Love with the Villainess
subTitle: Rei Ohashi, an overworked employee, passes away after which she is reincarnated as Rae Taylor, her favourite video game's heroine, and gets attracted to Claire Francois, the main antagonist.

title: Spider-Man 2
subTitle: After losing his job, lover and his powers, Peter Parker feels dissatisfied with his life. Soon, amidst all this chaos, he also has to fight Doctor Octavius who poses a threat to the New York.

title: Charlie's Angels: Full Throttle
subTitle: The Angels track down rings containing the names of those in the FBI's witness protection programme. However, the witnesses begin to get murdered one by one.

title: 12 Mighty Orphans
subTitle: A passionate football coach sees potential in a group of orphaned teenagers. So, he starts training them for a state championship, inspiring hope during the Great Depression.

title: It Ends With Us
subTitle: A woman's relationship with a charismatic but violent neurosurgeon is thrown in shambles by the sudden arrival of her first love.

title: The Taking of Pelham 123
subTitle: A subway dispatcher's day is thrown into chaos when four armed men hijack the subway train and take the commuters as hostages. They demand USD 10 million from the mayor as ransom.

title: Venom: The Last Dance
subTitle: As Eddie and Venom are tirelessly pursued by forces from both of their worlds, they find themselves out of options and left with a shattering last resort.

title: Anacondas: The Hunt for the Blood Orchid
subTitle: A team of researchers is in Borneo to find the blood orchid, a flower that could hold the secret to eternal life. However, the scientists run afoul of the jungle's deadly snakes.

title: XXX
subTitle: The US government recruits extreme sports athlete Xander Cage to infiltrate a Russian criminal ring, which is plotting the destruction of the world.

title: XXX: State of the Union
subTitle: Darius Stone, a former US Navy SEAL, is recruited as a new agent in the XXX programme to stop a rogue military faction from overthrowing the US government.

title: White House Down
subTitle: When terrorists suddenly invade the White House, police officer John Cale springs into action to protect his daughter and the President of the United States.

title: Hotel Transylvania 2
subTitle: Count Dracula is overjoyed to witness the birth of his grandson, Dennis. However, when Dennis shows no signs of being a vampire, Dracula tries to help him unlock his powers.

title: Anaconda
subTitle: A documentary crew, who are on a mission to find a tribe named Shirishamas, help a snake hunter when they find him stranded. However, he forces them to risk their lives and hunt down an anaconda.

subTitle: Columbus, Tallahassee, Wichita and Little Rock set out on a mission to protect the rest of humanity by fighting evolved zombies while also battling their own internal demons.
